<CENTER>
<TABLE width="85%">
<TR>
<TD>

<P>Conan and Lana, the main characters in
<I>Conan,</I> are often considered prototypes of 
<A href="../laputa/">Laputa's</A> Pazu and Sheeta.</p>

<P>The official (from the Japanese creators) 
English title for this TV series is <I>Conan, The Boy in Future,</I> 
though this is an incorrect English rendition of the Japanese title. 
Anime fans usually call this series <I>Future Boy Conan,</I> which is 
much easier to remember and say.</p>

<p>Mirai Shounen Conan 2 - Taiga Daiboken (Future Boy Conan 2 - River Adventure) does not 
have any Miyazaki/Studio Ghibli involvement.</p>
<BR>&nbsp;

</TD>
</TR>
